Searching.description: Heart on hypem: http://hypem.com/track/2gnv7 Hello deep house lovers, Aux Deep is back with an incredible premiere, born ready for your summer playlists. We return with two of our great friends, @chrisvivianoofficial x @officialsjur - these two Norweigan talents put an incredible spin of Alan Walker's classic track, Faded. Strap in your seatbelts for the huge piano-fuelled drops layered so sweetly with those explosive synths. This tune is served best with jaw-dropping decibels. Enjoy, Aux boys.
